msgstr ""
":menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings`に移動し"
"、:guilabel:`eCommerce`セクションまでスクロールして、:guilabel:`Product "
"Reference Price`を有効にします。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:56
msgid ""
":ref:`Navigate to the product form <ecommerce/products/product-creation>`."
msgstr ":ref:`プロダクトフォームに移動 <ecommerce/products/product-creation>`します。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:57
msgid ""
"Set the product's :guilabel:`Sales Price` and select the unit "
"(e.g., :guilabel:`Units`)."
msgstr ""
"プロダクトの:guilabel:`Sales Price`を設定し、単位(例::guilabel:`Units`)を選択"
