#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:3
msgid "Domain names"
msgstr "ドメイン名"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:5
msgid ""
"Domain names serve as easily recognizable labels for online locations such "
"as websites, translating difficult-to-remember numerical IP addresses into "
"readable, memorable web addresses."
msgstr ""
"ドメイン名は、ウェブサイトなどのオンライン上の場所を示す覚えやすいラベルとし"
"て機能し、記憶しにくい数値のIPアドレスを読みやすく覚えやすいウェブアドレスに"
"変換します。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:8
msgid ""
":doc:`Odoo Online <../../../../administration/odoo_online>` "
"and :doc:`Odoo.sh <../../../../administration/odoo_sh>` databases use a "
"subdomain of the `odoo.com` domain by default (e.g., `mycompany.odoo.com`)."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Odoo Online <../../../../administration/odoo_online>`と:doc:`Odoo.sh "
"<../../../../administration/odoo_sh>`データベースは、デフォルト"
"で`odoo.com`ドメインのサブドメインを使用します(例:`mycompany.odoo.com`)。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:12
msgid ""
"However, you can :ref:`register a free domain name <domain-name/register>` "
"on Odoo Online or :ref:`use a domain name you own <domain-name/existing>`."
msgstr ""
"ただし、Odoo Onlineで:ref:`無料ドメイン名を登録 <domain-name/register>`するか"
"、:ref:`所有するドメイン名を使用 <domain-name/existing>`することができます。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:16
