#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:98
msgid ""
"All installed website-related apps (e.g., eCommerce, eLearning, Forum, etc.) "
"and their related pages are also available on the new website. You can "
"remove them from the website's menu."
msgstr ""
"インストールされたすべてのウェブサイト関連アプリ(eコマース、Eラーニング、"
